---
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Designs" pageTitle="Tattoo Styles">
  <!-- Spacer to push content below the fixed navbar -->
  <div class="h-40"></div>

  <!-- Main content with width + horizontal padding -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Tattoo Styles We Offer</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">
      At Jackfrost Tattoo, our specialty lies in minimalist and fine-line work. Every design is crafted with clarity and intention—built to last and made to speak.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-8">
      <li><strong>Fine-line Minimalism</strong> – Clean, delicate lines with subtle depth and precision.</li>
      <li><strong>Script Tattoos</strong> – Names, phrases, and personal mantras in elegant, flowing type.</li>
      <li><strong>Geometric Art</strong> – Bold symmetry and sacred shapes for timeless statement pieces.</li>
      <li><strong>Microrealism</strong> – Small-scale portraits or realistic elements that feel alive.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Consultations are always free. Whether you have a design in mind or need help shaping your vision, we’re here to collaborate with you every step of the way.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
